% ====================================================================
% test_bestagon_proto_mapgen.trx -- run examples/bestagon-proto/
% proto-mapgen.trx via the tests/ harness.
% ====================================================================
%
% Thin wrapper: loads proto-mapgen.trx (Phase 0.7: procedural map
% generator).  Algorithm: noise + cellular-automata + cluster-spawn
% + flood-fill connectedness with mirror-h / rotational-180 symmetry.
%
% 6 assertions: connectedness + seed-determinism for each of 3 sizes
% (Tutorial 25x18, Standard 50x36, Epic 75x54) over 10 random seeds.
%
% Throws on any assertion mismatch.  Runs on default 1 MB VM.  On
% debug build: ~3-4 min (the bench dominates).  On prod: ~10-15 s
% (mean 41/175/402 ms per generation across the 3 sizes).
% ====================================================================

(examples/bestagon-proto/proto-mapgen.trx) run
(__test_ok__) =
